message.content: cs.SD, cs.SD is the sub-category for Sound and Music Computing, which is the most relevant sub-category for this paper as it deals with Acoustic Event Detection. Other likely sub-categories could be cs.CL (Computation and Language) as the paper deals with attention-based methods, cs.LG (Machine Learning) as the paper proposes a new module for AED, cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition) as the paper deals with image-like representations of sound, and cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) as the paper proposes a new method for AED.
